Algorithm: Ordering Food on Swiggy

1. **Start.**
2. Open the **Swiggy** app.
3. Log in to your account (if required).
4. Allow or select your delivery location.
5. Search for a restaurant or food item.
6. Select the restaurant.
7. Browse the menu.
8. Choose the food items you want to order.
9. Add the selected items to the cart.
10. Review your cart and make changes if needed.
11. Tap **Proceed to Checkout**.
12. Confirm the delivery address.
13. Apply a coupon code (optional).
14. Select your preferred payment method (UPI, Credit/Debit Card, Net Banking, Wallet, or Cash on Delivery, if available).
15. Complete the payment.
16. Wait for the payment to be confirmed.
17. Receive the order confirmation and estimated delivery time.
18. **Stop.**

